from my perception.

00:46:39.800 --> 00:46:44.860
I think Long COVID
puts a lot into this.

00:46:47.310 --> 00:46:55.310
Any viral infection gives
internal stress, and COVID,

00:46:55.350 --> 00:46:58.810
as a virus infection,
is also tailoring to this.

00:47:00.190 --> 00:47:04.080
I saw a lot of people
mentioning that also Long COVID

00:47:04.080 --> 00:47:09.920
is raising the disability numbers.

00:47:09.920 --> 00:47:15.600
And I think it contributes to
this number, Long COVID, Yes.

